text: Mulshi is a village and an administrative block in Pune district, Maharashtra, India. Mulshi may also refer to: * Mulshi Dam, a dam on the Mula River in Pune district, Maharashtra, India * Mulshi taluka, an administrative division of the Pune district, Maharashtra, India ==See also== * Mulshi Kh., a village in Pune district, Maharashtra, India
title: Mulshi (disambiguation)
